Level 3 operators
-----------------

 [/] shfill (ShadingTypes 2, 3, 4 and 5; sampled functions at byte
     depths)
 [/] composite fonts (Type 0 FMapType 9 through composefont; CIDFont
     descendants of CIDFontType 2, incremental GlyphDirectory
     delivery, and CIDFontType 0, charstrings through StartData;
     cshow rebinds the composite to one-byte codes)
 [X] clipsave
 [X] cliprestore
 [X] setsmoothness, currentsmoothness (recorded only)
 [X] findcolorrendering (names the default instance)

